def myfun1(x,tissue):
    if x["0"]==tissue:
        return x["log2FoldChange"]
    elif x["1"]==tissue:
        return -1*x["log2FoldChange"]
spf_concat = pd.DataFrame()
for tissue in tissues:
    f1 = df_concat[df_concat["sample"].str.contains(tissue)]
    d1 = dict(f1["transcript_name"].value_counts())
    f1["val"] = f1["transcript_name"].map(lambda x: d1.get(x))
    f1 = f1[f1['val']==6]
    f1["lfc"] = f1.apply(lambda x: myfun1(x,tissue),axis=1)
    f1 = f1[f1["lfc"]>1]
    f1 = f1.drop_duplicates("transcript_name")
    f1["tissue"] = tissue
    spf_concat = pd.concat([f1,spf_concat])
    print("tissue-spf number ",tissue,f1.shape[0])

    if x["0"]==tissue:

        else :
            return "down"
    if x["1"]==tissue:

            return "up"
        else :
            return "down"

        return -1*x["log2FoldChange"]

    row = i // 3
    col = i % 3
    ax = axes[row, col]
    t1 = pd.read_csv(f'enrichment/{tissue}.tsv', sep="\t")
    t1 = t1.head(10)
    t1["-log10Padj"] = -1 * np.log10(t1["p.adjust"])

%%time
os.chdir("/home/zhaoying/workbai/NC/02.Quantification/NGS")
ngs = pd.DataFrame()
for file in os.listdir():
    if os.path.isdir(file):
        t1 = pd.read_csv(f'{file}/abundance.tsv',sep="\t")
        t1["sample"] = file
        ngs = pd.concat([ngs,t1])
#         print(file)
#         break
ngs = ngs[ngs["tpm"]>0.1]

ngs["tissue"] = ngs["sample"].str.split("-").map(lambda x: x[1])
ngs["sample"] = ngs["sample"].str.replace("sample","S")
ngs_groupped = ngs.groupby(["target_id","tissue"])["tpm"].agg('mean')

ngs_groupped = ngs_groupped.reset_index().pivot(index="target_id",columns="tissue",values="tpm")

ngs_groupped.to_csv("NGS_tpm_tissues.tsv",sep="\t")

ngs_pivot = ngs.pivot(index="target_id",columns="sample",values='tpm')

ngs_pivot.to_csv("NGS_tpm_samples.tsv",sep="\t")
